ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> So how many targets can that AE hit?</span><hr size=1> Thanks to a nice bug with SOL I got to finally find an answer tonight : ). The entire Tenebrous zone was being horribly lagged by a bug with Hoppers pets. There were actually 100 of them all stacked on top of each other. You could barely walk because the 100 pets were all casting at the same time. So Mr. Happy Wizard me lags his way next to them and after one cast of Winds the zone was fixed, 98 mob corpses on the ground. My zone buffer was too full to scroll out and find out why 2 weren't killed. The tracker that was counting got a good laugh out of it. <br>
<br>
Wonder if that's a record of some sort? : )  98 mobs killed in one cast. hehe<br>
<br>
Tutmos Howitzer<br>
Sorcerer Valoran<br>
Karana <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uglasya7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glasya7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/01 7:10:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9141.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: So how many targets can that AE hit?</span><hr size=1> Depends of which AOE, mages and wizards get PBAOE that affects any # of MOBs in the area.  Chanter AOE stun affects any # of MOBs, but Gflux only 4.  Rain spells only affect up to 4, and druid/cleric/necro/etc AOEs also affect only 4.  This is why for PBAOE groups only mages and wizards are needed for damage and chanters for stun, with other classes doing support work.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usouthernkreuz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Southern Kreuz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/01 8:21:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9141.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> heyo</span><hr size=1> .....it was a rhetorical question and i think he posted the answer himself hehe<br>
